### Unsplash API Tests for TriviaSpark
### Base URL: https://localhost:14165/api/unsplash (when running locally)

@baseUrl = https://localhost:14165/api

### Test 1: Search for wine-related images
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/search?query=wine&page=1&perPage=10
Accept: application/json

### Test 2: Search by specific category
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/categories/wine?page=1&perPage=5
Accept: application/json

### Test 3: Get featured images
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/featured?page=1&perPage=10
Accept: application/json

### Test 4: Search with filters (color and orientation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/search?query=landscape&color=blue&orientation=landscape&perPage=5
Accept: application/json

### Test 5: Get specific image by ID (replace with actual image ID from search results)
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/images/sample-image-id
Accept: application/json

### Test 6: Get image selection format (replace with actual image ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/images/sample-image-id/selection?size=regular
Accept: application/json

### Test 7: Get available categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/categories
Accept: application/json

### Test 8: Track download (replace with actual download URL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/track-download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "downloadUrl": "https://api.unsplash.com/photos/sample-id/download?ixid=sample-tracking-id"
}

### Test 9: Search for food-related images
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/categories/food?page=1&perPage=8
Accept: application/json

### Test 10: Search for science-related images with specific filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/unsplash/search?query=laboratory science&orderBy=latest&perPage=12
